# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Claude Command Center — environment configuration
# Copy to `.env` and adjust:  cp .env.sample .env
# All values have sensible localhost-first defaults; everything binds 127.0.0.1.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# --- Claude Agent SDK auth ---------------------------------------------------
# The Agent SDK authenticates one of two ways:
#   1. ANTHROPIC_API_KEY — a raw API key (uncomment + set below).
#   2. Local Claude CLI / subscription session — if you already run Claude Code
#      and are logged in, LEAVE ANTHROPIC_API_KEY UNSET and the SDK reuses that
#      session. This is the DEFAULT path (no key required).
#
# GOTCHA (see project memory / MoodBoarder): if a stale ANTHROPIC_API_KEY in
# your shell triggers "Credit balance too low", run the orchestrator with the
# key stripped:  `env -u ANTHROPIC_API_KEY bun run dev`.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# --- Ports (bind to 127.0.0.1 only) ------------------------------------------
ORCH_PORT=4100
WEB_PORT=3000

# --- Repo / workspace --------------------------------------------------------
# Absolute path to the repository Claude Code operates on + the file watcher
# tracks. Defaults to the current working directory if unset.
REPO_ROOT=/Users/you/path/to/repo

# --- Model defaults ----------------------------------------------------------
# Default model for newly-created agent sessions.
DEFAULT_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8

# --- Database ----------------------------------------------------------------
# SQLite file (Drizzle + bun:sqlite). Relative paths resolve from orchestrator/.
CC_DB_PATH=./command-center.db

# --- GitHub poller -----------------------------------------------------------
# Interval (ms) for the read-only gh/git poller.
GH_POLL_MS=30000

# --- Misc --------------------------------------------------------------------
NODE_ENV=development
LOG_LEVEL=info
